&lt;h2 id="sec-1"&gt;Separating sentences&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
In LaTeX, in order to separate two sentences one needs to
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol class="org-ol"&gt;
